			"content": {
				"number": "1",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"77906\"></a>Sjukdomar som kan vara orsaken  till förhöjda levervärden",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Se Figur 1 f&ouml;r information om utredning</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Parenkymat&ouml;sa leversjukdomar</strong>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Aminotransferaser och GT</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Fettlever:<br>Alkoholinducerad<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><br>&Ouml;vervikt</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>Kronisk hepatit:<br>Hepatit C<br>Hepatit B</li>\r\n<li>Autoimmun hepatit</li>\r\n<li>Hemokromatos</li>\r\n<li>Alfa-1-antitrypsinbrist</li>\r\n<li>L&auml;kemedel inkl h&auml;lsokostpreparat</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Aminotransferaser samt ALP och GT</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Prim&auml;r bili&auml;r cirros</li>\r\n<li>L&auml;kemedelsskador</li>\r\n<li>Akut virushepatit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Fokala f&ouml;r&auml;ndringar</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Aminotransferaser samt oftast ALP och GT</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Hemangiom<sup>a</sup></li>\r\n<li>Cystor<sup>b</sup></li>\r\n<li>Fokal nodul&auml;r hyperplasi</li>\r\n<li>Adenom</li>\r\n<li>Hepatocellul&auml;r cancer</li>\r\n<li>Metastaser</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Gallv&auml;gssjukdomar</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Aminotransferaser samt ALP och GT</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Koledokussten</li>\r\n<li>Gallg&aring;ngscancer</li>\r\n<li>Pankreascancer</li>\r\n<li>Prim&auml;r skleroserande kolangit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"1\" class=\"footNotes\">\r\n<div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_13\">a. <span class=\"tabstop\"></span>Hemangiom ger inte f&ouml;rh&ouml;jda leverprover utan uppt&auml;cks som bifynd vid ultraljud eller datortomografiunders&ouml;k&shy;ning.</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_14\">b. <span class=\"tabstop\"></span>Cystor kan ses med eller utan f&ouml;rh&ouml;jda leverv&auml;rden. Ultraljud ger god v&auml;gledning om typen av cysta.</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
				"id": "b2_8"
			},
