		{
			"id": "94ce7dbf-d7db-4707-8e3d-627b96ebf7dd",
			"name": "94ce7dbf-d7db-4707-8e3d-627b96ebf7dd",
			"type": "therapy",
			"content": {
				"number": "1",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"58013\"></a>Virushepatiter",
				"id": "b2_22",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hepatit</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Terapi</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Profylax</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hepatit A</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&ndash;</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Preexeposition</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vaccination,<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> i vissa fall <span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">gammaglobulin</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Postexposition</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Vaccination,<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> i vissa fall gammaglobulin</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hepatit B</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>(6)</strong></span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Interferon alfa, tenofovir eller entecavir vid</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">kronisk progressiv sjukdom</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Preexposition</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-style: italic;\"></span>Vaccination</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Postexposition</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Vaccination, specifikt immunglobulin</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hepatit C</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>(9)</strong></span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"updated\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Akut hepatit C ska inte behandlas.<br><br></span></p>\r\n<p>Nu finns ett antal direktverkande antivirala l&auml;kemedel mot hepatit C som tillh&ouml;r olika substansklasser och kombineras enligt s&auml;rskilda regler. Dessa anv&auml;nds vid m&aring;ttlig till allvarlig kronisk sjukdom.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&ndash;</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hepatit D</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>(Interferon alfa)\r\n<p></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Preexposition</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vaccination mot hepatit B</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hepatit E</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&ndash;</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&ndash;</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
			},
