		{
			"id": "f9169c95-b60e-4efe-9da2-039477e4e224",
			"name": "f9169c95-b60e-4efe-9da2-039477e4e224",
			"type": "therapy",
			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"title": "Behandling av komplikationer till levercirros",
				"id": "b2_67",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Bl&ouml;dning fr&aring;n esofagusvaricer</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&Ouml;vervakning p&aring; intensivv&aring;rdsavdelning: <span class=\"tab\"></span>puls, blodtryck och andning. <span class=\"tab\"></span>V&auml;tska intraven&ouml;st och blod (Hb ska vara cirka 80 g/l) ges efter behov.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class=\"index\" id=\"1026329\" data-text=\"oktreotid:esofagusvaricer\"></a>Oktreotid 25 mikrog/timme intraven&ouml;st i infu<span class=\"tab\"></span>sion medan bl&ouml;dning p&aring;g&aring;r. <span class=\"tab\"></span>Alternativt <a class=\"index\" id=\"1026331\" data-text=\"terlipressin\"></a>terlipressin 2 mg intra&shy;ven&ouml;st var 4:e <span class=\"tab\"></span>timme.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Akut gastroskopi f&ouml;r diagnostik och bandligering, <span class=\"tab\"></span>alternativt sklerosering.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Profylaktisk antibiotikabehandling med <a class=\"index\" id=\"1026333\" data-text=\"cefotaxim:esofagusvaricer\"></a>cefo<span class=\"tab\"></span>taxim, 1&nbsp;g intraven&ouml;st 2 g&aring;nger/dag.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Behandling av <a class=\"index\" id=\"1026336\" data-text=\"ascites\"></a>ascites</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>V&auml;tskerestriktion: 1&nbsp;500&ndash;2&nbsp;000 ml/dygn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Saltrestriktion vid sp&auml;nd ascites.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class=\"index\" id=\"1026340\" data-text=\"spironolakton:ascites\"></a>Spironolakton 50&ndash;400 mg/dag, <span class=\"tab\"></span><a class=\"index\" id=\"1026342\" data-text=\"furosemid:ascites\"></a>furosemid 40&ndash;160 mg/dag.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span><a class=\"index\" id=\"1026343\" data-text=\"laparocentes\"></a>Laparocentes: Om det t&ouml;mmer sig mer &auml;n 3 l ascites, substituera med <a class=\"index\" id=\"1026345\" data-text=\"albumin\"></a>albumin intraven&ouml;st <span class=\"tab\"></span>(8 g/l ascites).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Transjugular intrahepatisk portosystemisk shunt <span class=\"tab\"></span>(TIPS) anv&auml;nds i utvalda diuretikaresistenta fall.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Behandling av portosystemisk encefalopati</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Vaken patient: <span class=\"tab\"></span><a class=\"index\" id=\"1026350\" data-text=\"laktulos:leverencefalopati\"></a>Laktulos 10&ndash;30 ml 2&ndash;3 g&aring;nger/dygn. <span class=\"tab\"></span>Patienten ska ha 2 halvfasta avf&ouml;ringar/dygn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>P&aring;verkad somnolent eller medvetsl&ouml;s patient: <span class=\"tab\"></span>Uteslut annan orsak till medvetandep&aring;verkan. <span class=\"tab\"></span>Laktulos 30 ml i ventrikelsond upprepade g&aring;nger tills patienten f&aring;r avf&ouml;ring.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Laktuloslavemang (100 ml laktulos + 900 ml vatten), om inte peroral administration ger effekt. <span class=\"tab\"></span><a class=\"index\" id=\"1033487\" data-text=\"metronidazol:leverencefalopati\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Metronidazol peroralt, 400 mg 2&ndash;3 g&aring;nger/dag.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class=\"index\" id=\"1043476\" data-text=\"rifaximin:leverencefalopati\"></a>Rifaximin kan ges som profylax i upp till 6 m&aring;nader i dosen 550 mg 2 g&aring;nger/dag (se produktresum&eacute;/Fass).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
			},
